data.description: Experience the charm of this two-story home located in the heart of New Braunfels. Boasting exquisite curb appeal, this residence welcomes you with a modern aesthetic and a layout designed for comfort and functionality. The main living areas feature stunning wood-like flooring, creating an inviting atmosphere that flows seamlessly throughout. The contemporary kitchen is a haven for culinary enthusiasts, featuring ample cabinetry and countertop prep space for your creations. With three bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, this home provides plenty of room for both privacy and gatherings. Plush carpeting adds a touch of coziness to the bedrooms, offering a soothing retreat. Step outside to the covered patio, a perfect place to unwind and enjoy the outdoors. The generous backyard is a canvas awaiting your personal touch, ready to be transformed into your dream outdoor oasis. This property not only offers a comfortable living space but also the opportunity to make it your own in a desirable location. Schedule your private tour today and envision yourself in this dream home today!
